data.description: Recently renovated and move in ready 4Br/2Ba home, located in the sought- after lake subdivision of Turtle Cove in Jackson Lake. Renovations include new roof, new floors, new windows, new AC, new granite countertops, new lighting fixtures, new plumbing, new bathroom fixtures, new porch, new electrical system, new paint... The main home features 3 bedrooms and one full bathroom. The in-law suite consists of 1 bedroom, one full bathroom, and it's own kitchen. The amenities on this subdivision include: a golf course, tennis courts, club house, restaurant, bar, swimming-pool, playgrounds, several beaches, and boat ramps. This home is a must see!! Come check it out today!!
